pages.text:
Events
Howl-O-Ween  With Do Like Raleigh Roo
Sunday October 5th
Time to reveal those spooky and silly Howl-o-Ween costumes!  Join us with the Do Like Raleigh Roo Foundation and bring your ghostly goblin pups to Howl @ The Honu for our Howl-o-Ween extravaganza.   Raffles & drink specials   $5 entry for the costume contest with prizes for Silliest, Scariest, & Best Duo!   $20 professional photo-op by Dorky Daisy Photography (1 digital image)    See less
02:00 PM - 04:00 PM
Miss Honu Pageant 2025
Sunday October 19th
Join us for the 2025 Miss Honu Pinup Contest, presented by Mayzie Mac! There will be live music from Big Tiki & The Mai Tais, Delicious Tiki Drinks, and plenty of Beautiful Pinup Girls!
02:00 PM - 05:00 PM
Pineapple Carving  at The Honu
Friday October 24th
You're Invited to The Honu's Annual Pineapple Carving Party!
Join us for a fun-filled evening of creativity and community! This family-friendly event is open to all ages (adult supervision required). For only $10 per (pre-cored) pineapple, you can carve your own masterpiece while supporting a great cause.
Proceeds will benefit the Suncoast Animal League.
We can't wait to see you there!
06:00 PM - 09:00 PM
Rhum Barbancourt Halloween Pre-Party Cocktail Hour
Friday October 31st
Step into the spirit of the season during our pre-party cocktail hour in the Ka Pakele Rum Bar, hosted in partnership with Rhum Barbancourt and Florida Rum Society   Location: Ka Pakele Rum Bar (Located inside The Honu Restaurant)  Enjoy an exclusive cocktail menu featuring Rhum Barbancourt, highlighting the depth and versatility of one of the world’s finest Haitian rums. Passed hors d'oeuvres will also be served to compliment the Rhum offerings. Space is limited. Early arrival is recommended.
04:00 PM - 06:00 PM
HONUWEEN 2025
Friday October 31st
Save the Date for Honuween 2025, presented by Rhum Barbancourt and The Florida Rum Society. Get ready for a one-of-a-kind celebration inspired by Haitian Vodou culture. Rhum Barbancourt is pulling out all the stops for a Halloween party and Costume Contest, unlike anything you've experienced before. Stay tuned, more details coming soon!
07:00 PM - 10:00 PM
